query: WITH    rows AS (      SELECT id      FROM net.http_request_queue      ORDER BY id      LIMIT $1    )    DELETE FROM net.http_request_queue q    USING rows WHERE q.id = rows.id    RETURNING q.id, q.method, q.url, timeout_milliseconds, array(select key || $2 || value from jsonb_each_text(q.headers)), q.body

WITH    rows AS (      SELECT ctid      FROM net._http_response      WHERE created < now() - $1      ORDER BY created      LIMIT $2    )    DELETE FROM net._http_response r    USING rows WHERE r.ctid = rows.ctid

select set_config('search_path', $1, true), set_config('role', $2, true), set_config('request.jwt.claims', $3, true), set_config('request.method', $4, true), set_config('request.path', $5, true), set_config('request.headers', $6, true), set_config('request.cookies', $7, true)

SELECT t0."id", t0."name", t0."external_id", t0."jwt_secret", t0."jwt_jwks", t0."postgres_cdc_default", t0."max_concurrent_users", t0."max_events_per_second", t0."max_presence_events_per_second", t0."max_payload_size_in_kb", t0."max_bytes_per_second", t0."max_channels_per_client", t0."max_joins_per_second", t0."suspend", t0."private_only", t0."migrations_ran", t0."broadcast_adapter", t0."inserted_at", t0."updated_at" FROM "tenants" AS t0 WHERE (t0."external_id" = $1)

SELECT e0."id", e0."type", e0."settings", e0."tenant_external_id", e0."inserted_at", e0."updated_at", e0."tenant_external_id" FROM "extensions" AS e0 WHERE (e0."tenant_external_id" = $1) ORDER BY e0."tenant_external_id"

WITH pgrst_source AS ( SELECT "public"."bootcamp_programs".* FROM "public"."bootcamp_programs"  WHERE  "public"."bootcamp_programs"."id" = $1   LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3 )  SELECT $4::bigint AS total_result_set, pg_catalog.count(_postgrest_t) AS page_total, coalesce(json_agg(_postgrest_t)->$5, $6) AS body, nullif(current_setting($7, $8), $9) AS response_headers, nullif(current_setting($10, $11), $12) AS response_status, $13 AS response_inserted FROM ( SELECT * FROM pgrst_source ) _postgrest_t

WITH pgrst_source AS ( SELECT "public"."cohorts".* FROM "public"."cohorts"  WHERE  "public"."cohorts"."id" = $1   LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3 )  SELECT $4::bigint AS total_result_set, pg_catalog.count(_postgrest_t) AS page_total, coalesce(json_agg(_postgrest_t)->$5, $6) AS body, nullif(current_setting($7, $8), $9) AS response_headers, nullif(current_setting($10, $11), $12) AS response_status, $13 AS response_inserted FROM ( SELECT * FROM pgrst_source ) _postgrest_t

WITH pgrst_source AS ( SELECT "public"."bootcamp_enrollments"."id", row_to_json("bootcamp_enrollments_cohort_1".*)::jsonb AS "cohort" FROM "public"."bootcamp_enrollments" LEFT JOIN LATERAL ( SELECT "cohorts_1"."id", "cohorts_1"."bootcamp_program_id" FROM "public"."cohorts" AS "cohorts_1"  WHERE "cohorts_1"."id" = "public"."bootcamp_enrollments"."cohort_id"   LIMIT $1 OFFSET $2 ) AS "bootcamp_enrollments_cohort_1" ON $6 WHERE  "public"."bootcamp_enrollments"."user_profile_id" = $3   LIMIT $4 OFFSET $5 )  SELECT $7::bigint AS total_result_set, pg_catalog.count(_postgrest_t) AS page_total, coalesce(json_agg(_postgrest_t), $8) AS body, nullif(current_setting($9, $10), $11) AS response_headers, nullif(current_setting($12, $13), $14) AS response_status, $15 AS response_inserted FROM ( SELECT * FROM pgrst_source ) _postgrest_t
